I1MDM5Mjc2Nw==&mid=2247485042&idx=1&sn=7f0c4b18cc2228417dc1e3f48d8f0383&chksm=e983bfa2def436b4842d53ccf59e328711d4bd31f60e7ec44073f24ee7c58dcd5a28f37cdedf&scene=21#wechat_redirect)\\n\\n![]()\\n\\n现在微信公众号打乱了时间线，如果你不特地点进来，很可能看不到本号了。希望喜欢【溯元育新】的读者朋友们将本号【设为星标★】，方便找到我们；也欢迎点击右下角的【在看】。\\n\\n![]()\\n\\n![]()\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640588170,\"title\":\"美、欧、印模式的三种底色丨溯元周报\"},\"digest\":\"-_aoA9iO6-TTcoy0rgrl5KVUh7gua_UoXL7ZMy60gGk\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x8a8b0bf3911F48D74c323246935880DAA9064bE2\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"kq3RzOFC7HhsaMUPdEEJlKUV9HKz_Rp5sq7C_WWLgrM\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"NuDxaETHc4Z2ZkZ5gyDVynXEXIjKXlj8JFmTWJe-PjU\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"8e2dn68IFudeEb6E-__K4_jnDU3qvaA8j1oCKCtT-M_nmhCAAYZrg5dSeBfIk-MXOndUCq-FG18OiAqYph2U_g\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xb2902e2f97cda407eb25c9afd71e6c79d3a3ea95d7e6c5281688fde185ba52f22f0188b0a347d99ebb1d84829334c71fc2bc2c5ccb9e9272f28acff50302c71b1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"kq3RzOFC7HhsaMUPdEEJlKUV9HKz_Rp5sq7C_WWLgrM\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"NuDxaETHc4Z2ZkZ5gyDVynXEXIjKXlj8JFmTWJe-PjU\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"-_aoA9iO6-TTcoy0rgrl5KVUh7gua_UoXL7ZMy60gGk\"}"